title: Sabse Bada Khiladi

subTitle: A series of comical complexities ensue when two men who look alike find themselves in numerous problems, leading to utter confusion.

title: Uriyadi 2

subTitle: Meenakshi, a young classical dancer who was born in a family of artists, is bitter about the lack of opportunity in India. However, Chandrashekhar changes her outlook and helps her grow.

subTitle: In a small rustic town in UP, two brothers, Nannu and Munnu, chose very different paths. While one chooses a life of crime, the other runs a coaching centre.

title: Fillers

subTitle: A young loan recovery agent gets entangled in an unexpected accident that turns his life upside down. To avert the crisis, he must find a way to handle the highly destructive threat.

title: Suhaag

subTitle: Fin and April's flight to New York City hits a hurricane that throws sharks into the air. They must now fight flying sharks to save the city from a weird shark-filled storm.
